These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  videographer, paramedic, freelancer, designer
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, russian, spanish, turkish
City: hamburg, marseilles, new-york, rome
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, ship, train, tram
 1. the colombian is on the left or right of the person traveling to new-york##3
 2. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the designer##1
 3. the videographer is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person traveling to rome is the russian##1
 5. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the train##5
 6. the colombian is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5
 7. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far left##1
 8. the person driving the train is somewhere to the left of the russian##5
 9. the freelancer is on the left or right of the spanish##3
10. the person traveling to rome is somewhere between the person driving the bike and the videographer##7
11. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
12. the turkish is somewhere to the right of the person driving the tram##5
13. the person driving the tram is the person traveling to rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Job   | designer    | paramedic | freelancer    | videographer   |
| Nationality   | colombian | spanish | russian | turkish |
| City           | marseilles       | new-york   | rome  | hamburg     |
| Transport     | bike      | train   | tram    | ship    |

