 2. the indonesian is somewhere to the right of the italian##5
 3. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to boston##5
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is the australian##1
 5. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
 6. the chinese is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to venice##5
 7. the person traveling to boston is somewhere between the person drinking soy-milk and the australian##7
 8. the person traveling to rome is in an odd position##4
 9. the person traveling to rome is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5
10. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
11. the chinese is the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |       3       |     4      |
