 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is not the person who's hobby is dancing##6
 9. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3
10. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
