 6. the townhouse house is somewhere to the left of the tower house##5
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person who's hobby is cooking##7
 9. the person who's birthday is in january is the person watching crime movies##1
10. the tower house is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
11. the person who's birthday is in august is not the person watching crime movies##6

