10. the person watching action movies is on the left of the french##1
11. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
12. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |       4       |
| Pet         | goldfish      | fish   | hamster   | mouse       |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | action    | disaster | mystery       |
| Nationality   | brazilian  | colombian | french   | malaysian     |
| Color         | aquamarine   | white    | ivory   | amber |

