.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-18::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, brazilian, indonesian, russian
City: new-york, venice, london, rome
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, drawing, hiking, reading
4 different pets are kept: cat, goldfish, hamster, rabbit
 1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the indonesian##1
 2. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to new-york##5
 3. the person who's hobby is reading is between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the hamster##2
 4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
 5. the person traveling to venice is not the owner of the goldfish##6
 6. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to london##5
 7. the russian is somewhere between the indian and the person traveling to rome##7
 8. the russian is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5
 9. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
10. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
11. the indian is the person traveling to london##1
12. the person traveling to london is not the owner of the hamster##6

.:: Answer ::.
