.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, soy-milk, water
There 4 different types of food: avocado, pumpkin, lemon, tomato
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, designer, police-officer, writer
House: tower, victorian, craftsman, farmhouse
 1. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5
 2. the tower house is between the person eating lemon and the architect##2
 3. the person eating avocado is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1
 5. the writer is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the victorian house is not the police-officer##6
 7. the police-officer is somewhere between the person eating tomato and the person eating avocado##7
 8. the tower house is not the person eating avocado##6
 9. the writer is not the person eating tomato##6
10. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the tower house##3
11. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
12. the person eating lemon is not the person drinking fanta##6
13. the police-officer is on the left of the writer##1
14. the architect is on the left or right of the tower house##3
15. the designer is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3        |      4      |
