.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-20::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, begonia, dahlia, orchid
House: tower, modern, cottage, ranch-style
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, pony, rabbit, snake
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, rowing, skiing, water-polo
 1. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5
 2. the cottage house is the person who growsdahlia##1
 3. the person who's sport is rowing is the owner of the snake##1
 4. the owner of the rabbit is between the person who growsorchid and the person who growsbegonia##2
 5. the tower house is somewhere to the right of the person who growsbegonia##5
 6. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere between the cottage house and the person who growsdaisy##7
 7. the person who growsorchid is somewhere to the left of the modern house##5
 8. the owner of the goldfish is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 9. the modern house is somewhere to the left of the tower house##5
10. the owner of the pony is on the far right##1
11. the person who's sport is skiing is in an even position##4
12. the tower house is somewhere to the right of the person who growsbegonia##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Flower   | orchid      | dahlia     | begonia   | daisy    |
| House     | ranch-style | cottage   | modern | tower |
| Pet     | snake        | rabbit     | goldfish  | pony      |
| Sport   | rowing       | water-polo | cricket   | skiing    |

 